snippet.title: DCappella - The Glory Days (From "Incredibles 2"/Audio Only)
snippet.description:
DCappella debut self-titled album available now!
Download: http://disneymusic.co/DCappellaAlbumDL
Streaming: http://disneymusic.co/DCappellaAlbum

DCappella's first ever North American tour is set to launch January 22nd, 2019 at the Florida Theatre in Jacksonville, FL. The multi-city trek is set to hit 40-US markets including Nashville, Brooklyn, Philadelphia, Chicago and the Los Angeles area. The tour features a contemporary production of new Deke Sharon arrangements of Disney classic and modern hits, bringing to life a truly unique a cappella experience. Skincare company, H2O+ Beauty is the co-sponsor of the national tour. Get your tickets now: http://dcappellalive.com/tour/

‘Friend Like Me’ Meet & Greet Experiences: https://www.cidentertainment.com/events/dcappella-tour/

Follow DCappella:
Instagram: http://instagram.com/dcappellamusic
Facebook: http://facebook.com/dcappellamusic
Twitter: http://twitter.com/dcappellamusic
Official Website: http://dcappellalive.com

DCappella is Disney Music Group’s new a cappella singing sensation consisting of 7 members: Sojourner Brown (alto), Orlando Dixon (baritone), Antonio Fernandez (vocal percussion), Morgan Keene (soprano), Shelley Regner (mezzo), Joe Santoni (bass), and RJ Woessner (tenor).
